meta {
  name: Lab Test Options
  type: http
  seq: 6
}

get {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/siteadmin/lab-tests/options?page=1&limit=10&search=
  body: none
  auth: bearer
}

params:query {
  page: 1
  limit: 10
  search:
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{siteAdminToken}}
}

docs {
  Lightweight `{ id, name }` options for SITE_ADMIN lab-test templates — feeds the
  Test Groups multi-select (`PaginatedSelect`) in the Site Admin FE. Auth:
  SiteAdmin token, requires `master-data:read`.

  Filters active, non-deleted templates (`source = SITE_ADMIN`, `tenantId = null`);
  `name` is the template's `testName`.

  Query params:
  - `page` / `limit` — **opt-in** offset pagination. Omit `page` to get the full
    `{ id, name }[]` array; supply `page` to get a paginated envelope (pagination
    info lands in `meta`, incl. `totalPages`).
  - `search` — case-insensitive match on `testName` (optional).

  **Sample response — 200 (paginated)**
  ```json
  {
    "success": true,
    "data": [
      { "id": "3f1a…lab-test-uuid-1", "name": "Complete Blood Count" },
      { "id": "9c2b…lab-test-uuid-2", "name": "Lipid Profile" }
    ],
    "meta": {
      "timestamp": "2026-07-01T09:00:00.000Z",
      "total": 2,
      "page": 1,
      "limit": 10,
      "totalPages": 1
    }
  }
  ```
}
